[{:name "Compelling Voice"
  "Axiom Level" 23
  :Skill "Telepathy 12"
  "Casting Time" "1 action"
  :DN "Hard (–4) vs. target’s willpower or Mind"
  :Range "5 meters"
  :Duration "1 round"
  :description "Compelling voice may only be manifested at
a single target, and the target must be able to
understand the psi (i.e. it must be intelligent
enough to understand commands and speak the
same language).
To manifest this power, the psi must speak a short
command to a single target (no Multi-Targeting).
The command may involve the victim undertaking
any action using his own skills and abilities, but
may not be forced to spend Possibilities. If the
command involves making multiple actions,
manifesting this power invokes a penalty equal to
the usual Multi-Action penalty. If the command
endangers the victim’s life (such as telling them to
walk off a cliff) the telepathy test takes an additional
Hard (–4) penalty.
If the target is reality-rated, the test is instead a
contest of telepathy vs. willpower or Spirit.
On a success, the target resists but becomes
Stymied and Vulnerable.
Success Levels:
• Good: The target must undertake the action,
but any skill tests to resolve the action take a –2
penalty.
• Outstanding: As Good but without penalty."}
 {:name "Heat Shield"
