  "Casting Time" "1 action"
  :DN "Standard (DN 10)"
  :Range "Self"
  :Duration "6 rounds"
  :description "The psi creates a shimmering wave of heat that
surrounds her, and incinerates projectiles (bullets,
arrows, etc.) fired at her. This shield has no effect
on melee or unarmed attacks, nor does it affect
energy weapons attacks. On a success, the hero gains
+2 to her dodge defense and +2 Armor against fire
combat and missile weapons attacks
Success Levels:
• Good: The bonuses increase to +3.
• Outstanding: The bonuses increase to +4."}
 {:name "Minor Telekinesis"
  "Axiom Level" 23
  :Skill "Kinesis 8"
  "Casting Time" "1 action"
  :DN "Easy (DN 8)"
  :Range "10 meters"
  :Duration "Concentration"
  :description "Minor telekinesis allows the psi to grasp, move,
and manipulate objects with a mass of up to five
kilograms with her mind. This can include such
actions as wielding a sword, flipping a switch,
or punching a foe. Although the psi can only
manipulate small objects (or barely push heavier
ones) if he strikes with those objects (or just with
his mind) it uses a base Strength equal to the psi’s
Spirit.
The psi must manifest this power to grasp or hold
a single object but once successfully manifested, he
may continue to manipulate that object as long as
he maintains Concentration. He may manipulate
other objects by manifesting the power additional
times.
The psi uses his own skills as normal (i.e. unarmed
combat when hitting a foe, lockpicking when
attempting to pick a lock).
Success Levels:
• Good: The psi may transfer focus to another
object without manifesting minor telekinesis
again.
• Outstanding: The duration increases to 6
rounds."}
 {:name "Teleport"
  "Axiom Level" 26
  :Skill "Kinesis 12"
  "Casting Time" "1 action"
  :DN "Standard (DN 10)"
  :Range "10 meters"
  :Duration "Instant"
  :description "With this power, the psi may transport herself,
her belongings and any small objects she holds
(but not other beings) directly to another location
within range. She can declare the target location
either generally (e.g. to the other side of the door)
or by direction and distance (e.g. 10 meters straight
up).
On a success, the psi teleports successfully but
is disoriented upon arrival and is Stymied and
Vulnerable.
The psi may teleport to locations she cannot see,
but the kinesis test takes a Hard (–4) penalty. If she
would accidentally appear in a solid she teleports
to the nearest safe location (within range, which
may include her origin point) but all tests are
Disfavored until the end of her next turn.
Success Levels:
• Good: The psi is not Stymied or Vulnerable
after teleporting.
• Outstanding: As Good and the psi’s next
attack against enemies in the vicinity are
Favored."}
